                    	<note xml:id="n_remarks" type="remarks">
                    	    
                                    
<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">The address ‘Den Heer E.H. Borchers <hi rend="italics">s’Hage</hi>’ written on the letter itself confirms that it was sent together with <ref target="let042.xml">letter 42</ref>. Van Gogh probably assumed that Borchers’s second Christian name was Hubertus, which is more usual than Rubertus.</p>
                                    
                                
