      <hi xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="italics">De opkomst van de Nederlandsche Republiek</hi>. The Hague 1859, a translation of <ref target="biblio.xml#lit_39"><hi rend="italics">The rise of the Dutch Republic. A history</hi></ref>. London 1856 by <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_714">John Lothrop Motley</rs>.</p>
